Text Post: It's very true that the backpropagation algorithm has been extremely influential and is used by almost all production models today, but I have always been shocked that anybody ever considered "deep learning" to be an invention. As a teenager in the 90s, long before I heard of Hinton, I built a spiking neural network that was many layers deep, inspired by human biology. I was most certainly not the only one who just copied the biological model as closely as possible.

Q-19: If you apply a dropout layer with a drop rate of 0.5 to a matrix of ones, you will see that some elements of the output matrix become zero, while the remaining elements are set to 2. Why?

Category: Deep Learning
Level: Medium 

A: To maintain the expected value of each element of the matrix to 1 (original value).

Text Post: Peccato che "la vita comincia dal concepimento" non e' un'affermazione basata sulla scienza ma sulle tue convinzioni etico-valoriali: rispettabili ma non scientifiche. La scienza dice che si puo' parlare di vita nel senso inteso comunemente (ossia senziente) o dalla formazione del sistema nervoso (intorno ai 3 mesi dal concepimento) o dallo sviluppo della coscienza (intorno alla ventottesima settimana).

You wanna see a certain movie, just make it with AI, you wanna hear certain music, just make it with AI, you want certain art, make it with AI. Paired food, adult entertainment, relationships, video games.

We will have to come up with new reasons to interact with each other.

Text Post: It's very true that the backpropagation algorithm has been extremely influential and is used by almost all production models today, but I have always been shocked that anybody ever considered "deep learning" to be an invention. As a teenager in the 90s, long before I heard of Hinton, I built a spiking neural network that was many layers deep, inspired by human biology. I was most certainly not the only one who just copied the biological model as closely as possible.

Q-19: If you apply a dropout layer with a drop rate of 0.5 to a matrix of ones, you will see that some elements of the output matrix become zero, while the remaining elements are set to 2. Why?

Category: Deep Learning
Level: Medium 

A: To maintain the expected value of each element of the matrix to 1 (original value).
